%% vllm-cpu Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6
%% Source: architecture/rhoai-3.0/vllm-cpu.md

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant KServe as KServe Router
    participant OpenAI as OpenAI API Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant TGIS as vllm-tgis-adapter<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant Engine as vLLM Engine<br/>(PagedAttention)
    participant CPU as CPU Worker<br/>(C/C++ Kernels)
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant S3 as S3/PVC Storage

    Note over Engine,HF: Flow 3: Model Loading (Startup)
    Engine->>HF: Download model weights<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: HF Token (optional)
    HF-->>Engine: Model artifacts & tokenizer
    Engine->>S3: Load from S3/PVC<br/>(alternative source)
    S3-->>Engine: Model weights
    Engine->>CPU: Load weights to CPU memory

    Note over Client,CPU: Flow 1: OpenAI-Compatible Inference
    Client->>KServe: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS (platform TLS)
    KServe->>OpenAI: HTTP/8000<br/>Optional TLS<br/>Auth: API Key (optional)
    OpenAI->>Engine: In-process call<br/>FastAPI handler
    Engine->>CPU: Execute inference<br/>CPU kernels
    CPU-->>Engine: Tensor results
    Engine-->>OpenAI: Completion response
    OpenAI-->>KServe: HTTP Response<br/>(streaming SSE supported)
    KServe-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over Client,CPU: Flow 2: gRPC TGIS Inference
    Client->>KServe: gRPC request
    KServe->>TGIS: gRPC/8033<br/>plaintext<br/>No auth
    TGIS->>Engine: In-process call<br/>TGIS protocol translation
    Engine->>CPU: Execute inference<br/>CPU kernels
    CPU-->>Engine: Tensor results
    Engine-->>TGIS: Inference result
    TGIS-->>KServe: gRPC Response<br/>(streaming supported)
    KServe-->>Client: gRPC Response
